casebody.data:
Friday, October 6, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

94-1389. Kendrick v. Cleveland Metroparks Bd. of Commrs.

Cuyahoga County, Nos. 65388 and 65525. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellants’ motion to extend time for oral argument scheduled for October 24, 1995,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to extend time for oral argument be, and hereby is, denied, effective October 3, 1995.
